{"metadata":{"name":"Sunan Ibn Majah","section":{"35":"Interpretation of Dreams"},"section_detail":{"35":{"hadithnumber_first":3893,"hadithnumber_last":3926,"arabicnumber_first":3893,"arabicnumber_last":3926}}},"hadiths":[{"hadithnumber":3913,"arabicnumber":3913,"text":"Rapporté par Jabir : Le Messager d’Allah (ﷺ) a dit : “Si l’un de vous fait un mauvais rêve, il ne doit pas raconter comment Satan a joué avec lui dans son rêve.”","grades":[{"name":"Al-Albani","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Muhammad Fouad Abd al-Baqi","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Shuaib Al Arnaut","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Zubair Ali Zai","grade":"Sahih Muslim"}],"reference":{"book":35,"hadith":21}}]}